name: All is Dreams
description: Hicetnunc is a space where my work feels free to dream. It is a space where the colours run looser and the forms melt and blend into a vista of dreamy nature. They are lucid here, living a life of their own through the veil. "All is Dreams" is a piece of work in it's dream state of the waking "All is love, All is one". This work is achieved by adding in another layer of experimentation in my work flow where I use the ai filters of deep dream and then bring them back to my editing process further
